lead_paragraph: The title of the lead-off panel on Monday at the Sefcon conference, a Wall Street gathering devoted to the relatively obscure world of the swap execution facility, asked a question that most people outside the financial industry would appreciate: "What is a S.E.F. and what is it good for?"

headline.main: Wall Street Goes to Sefcon II on Swaps
